" map configures
"
" see => :tab h map.txt
"---------------------------------

" like emacs (move)
inoremap <C-p> <UP>
inoremap <C-n> <DOWN>
inoremap <C-b> <LEFT>
inoremap <C-f> <RIGHT>
inoremap <C-a> <HOME>
inoremap <C-e> <END>

" like emacs (edit)
inoremap <C-h> <BS>
inoremap <C-d> <Del>
inoremap <C-w> <C-w>
inoremap <C-k> <C-o><S-d>
inoremap <C-u> <C-u>
